title: Oceanic University Championship top 9!
body:
http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/sites/default/files/styles/scale_xlarge/public/upload/002971_lol_luna_park_card3_1280x720px_02.jpg?itok=KJutZcky

We are down to our top 9 teams, one team from each respective region. You can find out more information on the [brackets page.](http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/oceanic-university-championship-playoffs)

**Group A**
New Zealand: University of Auckland - Dream
Victoria: Monash A
South Australia: University of South Australia - Succubus Tea Party
Northern Territory: Charles Darwin University - Engineers
Tasmania: University of Tasmania - Wood 7 Warriors

**Group B**
Australian Capital Territory: Australian National University - Super Five
Queensland: Queensland University of Technology - Team Zabuza
Western Australia: University of Western Australia - UWA
New South Wales: University of New South Wales - Team Phonezone
